159.question: What is typical GAN architecture for each text-to-image synhesis group?
159.response: {'Answer': 'DCGAN, GAN-INT-CLS, Dong-GAN, Paired-D GAN, StackGAN, StackGAN++, AttnGAN, Obj-GAN, HDGAN, DM-GAN, TACC-GAN, Tex-SeGAN, Scene Graph GAN, MirrorGAN'}
159.answer:
Semantic Enhancement GANs: DC-GANs, MC-GAN
